    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a rear-mounted limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed bushings, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback. Recent service includes a VANOS system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, maintaining optimal timing and compression. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity and linear power delivery remain uncompromising.",
