      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the slightest evidence of highway driving in the form of minor stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership: the leather seats are firm and free of cracks, the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one, and all interior trim pieces remain securely fastened. Every feature, including the heated seats, navigation system, and adaptive cruise control, has been tested and works perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This car drives straight, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet, refined ride. It is a complete package for someone seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
